\title{Adjoint Operator}
\date{2025-05-26}
\taxon{Definition}


\p{For a [bounded linear operator](FA-002G) A on a [Hilbert space](FA-000U) H, the adjoint operator #{A^*} satisfies #{\ \langle Ax,y\rangle = \langle x, A^*y\rangle} for all x, y in H.}

\p{An operator is [self-adjoint](FA-003L) if #{A = A^*}.}
